{
  "id": "l0_04",
  "course_id": "level_0",
  "order": 4,
  "title": "兵的走法",
  "description": "学习兵的前进、吃子、初始两步、吃过路兵和升变",
  "estimated_minutes": 18,
  "theme": {
    "bgGradient": "from-pink-50 to-rose-100",
    "accentColor": "#f43f5e"
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "content": "豆丁老师，棋盘上那些最矮的小个子棋子是什么呀？看起来好弱的样子。"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "那是兵！别小看它们哦，兵可是有大秘密的！每方各有8个兵，数量最多。"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "content": "大秘密？什么秘密呀？快告诉我！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "兵有4个特殊本领！直走斜吃、初始两步、吃过路兵，还有最厉害的——走到对面底线可以变身！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "content": "变身？！变成什么？变成奥特曼吗？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "哈哈，比奥特曼还厉害呢！兵可以变成王后！先来看看兵是怎么走路的吧。"
    },
    {
      "type": "board_demo",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "fen": "8/8/8/8/8/4P3/8/8 w - - 0 1",
      "description": "看这个白兵在e3。兵只能向前走，不能后退哦——它是个勇敢的小士兵！这个兵可以走到e4。",
      "highlights": [
        "e3",
        "e4"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "content": "只能往前走不能后退？那岂不是很勇敢！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "没错！而且兵在起始位置可以一下子走两格呢。来看看这个——"
    },
    {
      "type": "board_demo",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "fen": "8/8/8/8/8/3p1p2/4P3/8 w - - 0 1",
      "description": "白兵在e2，这是它的起始位置。它可以走到e3或e4（初始两步）。你知道吗？如果d3或f3有敌人，白兵还可以斜着把它吃掉呢！",
      "highlights": [
        "e2",
        "e3",
        "e4",
        "d3",
        "f3"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "content": "等等！兵直着走，却斜着吃？这也太奇怪了吧！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "对！记住口诀——\"直走斜吃\"！这就是兵最特别的地方。现在来看最激动人心的部分——升变！"
    },
    {
      "type": "board_demo",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "fen": "8/4P3/8/8/8/8/8/8 w - - 0 1",
      "description": "哇！白兵到达第7行了！再走一步到第8行，就可以升变啦！可以变成后、车、象或马。大多数时候我们选择变成后，因为后最强大！一个小兵变成了王后，是不是超酷？",
      "highlights": [
        "e7",
        "e8"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "celebrate",
      "content": "小兵变王后！太酷了！就像灰姑娘变公主一样！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "content": "还有一个特殊技能——吃过路兵，这个比较难，仔细看哦。"
    },
    {
      "type": "board_demo",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "fen": "8/8/8/4Pp2/8/8/8/8 w - f6 0 1",
      "description": "这个有点特别——吃过路兵！黑兵刚从f7走了两步到f5，经过了f6。白兵在e5可以\"假装\"黑兵停在了f6来吃掉它——这就是吃过路兵（en passant）。白兵吃到f6，f5的黑兵就被拿走了！",
      "highlights": [
        "e5",
        "f5",
        "f6"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "content": "哇，这招好厉害！就是说对方兵想偷偷溜过去，我可以半路拦截它？"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "理解得太对了！不过只能在对方刚走完两步的时候立刻吃，过了就没机会了。好了，来自己试试吧！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "celebrate",
      "content": "我能自己动手走棋吗？好期待呀！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "encourage",
      "content": "当然！先从最简单的开始——让白兵往前走一格！"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "encourage",
      "instruction": "把白兵往前走一格！从d3走到d4。",
      "fen": "8/8/8/8/8/3P4/8/4K2k w - - 0 1",
      "expectedMove": "d3d4",
      "hint": "点击d3的白兵，再点击d4"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "celebrate",
      "content": "耶！我做到了！兵往前走了一步！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "很好！现在试试兵在起始位置走两格！"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "encourage",
      "instruction": "白兵在起始位置，可以一下子走两格！试试走到d4！",
      "fen": "8/8/8/8/8/8/3P4/4K2k w - - 0 1",
      "expectedMove": "d2d4",
      "hint": "点击d2的白兵，再点击d4"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "一下子走了两格，好过瘾！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "content": "接下来是兵的特殊技能——斜吃！棋盘上有一个黑兵，把它吃掉！"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "encourage",
      "instruction": "白兵可以斜着吃掉黑兵！把白兵吃到c3！",
      "fen": "8/8/8/8/8/2p5/3P4/4K2k w - - 0 1",
      "expectedMove": "d2c3",
      "hint": "点击d2的白兵，再点击c3的黑兵位置"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "content": "直走斜吃！真的是这样呀！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "没错！你记住了口诀！来个更难的——白兵马上就要到底线变身了！"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "encourage",
      "instruction": "白兵马上就要到底线了！走到d8变成王后！",
      "fen": "8/3P4/8/8/8/8/8/4K2k w - - 0 1",
      "expectedMove": "d7d8",
      "hint": "点击d7的白兵，再点击d8——兵到底线会自动升变为王后"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "celebrate",
      "content": "小兵变王后！灰姑娘变身成功！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "最后一个挑战！白兵左右各有一个敌人，选一个吃掉吧！"
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "encourage",
      "instruction": "白兵左右各有一个敌人，选一个吃掉吧！",
      "fen": "8/8/8/8/2p1p3/3P4/8/4K2k w - - 0 1",
      "expectedMove": "d3c4",
      "hint": "白兵可以斜着吃左边c4或右边e4的黑兵——点击d3的白兵，再选一个吃掉"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "douding",
      "expression": "thinking",
      "content": "考考你，看你记住了兵的走法没有！"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "character": "xiaoqi",
      "expression": "happy",
      "content": "来吧，我准备好了！"
    },
    {
      "type": "quiz",
